<TEXT>
<P>
JMB Realty Corp. reportedly is bidding for Bloomingdale's department stores and 
Hilton Hotels Corp., and an industry analyst said Tuesday that both properties 
would mesh with the international firm's expansion strategy. 
</P>
<P>
JMB, a real estate investment, management and development firm, is one of at 
